    ],
    "text": "During the operation, officers recovered 9 kilograms and 128 grams of crystal methamphetamine (Ice), 03 anti-personnel landmines, 03 fuse components, 20 rounds of live M16 ammunition, 05 swords, an electronic weighing scale, and a motorcycle. A suspect was arrested and subsequently handed over to the Police Narcotics Bureau for further investigation.",
    "fonts": [
